    <style>
        .title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1rem;
        }

        .font {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 32px 16px 16px;
            color: rgba(69, 90, 100, 0.6);
            font-weight: normal;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 16px;
        }

        .video {
            padding: 0 5%;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        /*video默认aduio音量按钮*/
        video::-webkit-media-controls-mute-button {
            display: none !important;
        }

        .img {
            width: 5rem;
            height: 5rem;
        }


        .text {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }

        .bottom {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .text-center {
            margin-top: 4px;
            color: rgba(69, 90, 100, 0.6);
            font-weight: normal;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 16px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>

<body>
    <div id="app">
        <div class="title">刀子嘴豆腐干</div>

        <div class="font">水焖香干、凉伴香干做法</div>

        <video controls="controls" width="90%" class="video" controlsList='nodownload noremote footbar'
            src="https://hmvide.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/%E5%88%80%E5%AD%90%E5%98%B4ok.mp4">
            您的浏览器不支持 video 标签。
        </video>

        <van-grid :column-num="3">
            <van-grid-item>
                <van-image class="img" fit="cover" src="https://hmvide.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/q1.png" />
            </van-grid-item>
            <van-grid-item>
                <van-image class="img" fit="cover" src="https://hmvide.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/q2.png" />
            </van-grid-item>
            <van-grid-item>
                <van-image class="img" fit="cover" src="https://hmvide.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/q3.png" />
            </van-grid-item>
            <van-grid-item>
                <van-image class="img" fit="cover" src="https://hmvide.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/q4.png" />
            </van-grid-item>
            <van-grid-item>
                <van-image class="img" fit="cover" src="https://hmvide.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/q5.png" />
            </van-grid-item>
            <van-grid-item>
                <van-image class="img" fit="cover" src="https://hmvide.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/q6.png" />
            </van-grid-item>
        </van-grid>
        <div class="text">1.香干切薄片，沸水中煮2分钟让后捞干待用；</div>
        <div class="text">2.葱、蒜切粒;</div>
        <div class="text">3.热油，倒入到准备好的辣椒中，制作辣椒油；</div>
        <div class="text">4.在一个容器内，放入处理好的香干、辣椒油和葱花；</div>
        <div class="text">5.撒上少许盐、糖；</div>
        <div class="text">5.搅拌即可使用</div>

        <div class="bottom">

